    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with surgical precision via six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual, the drivetrain remains tight with a factory limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes comprehensive VANOS servicing and a rear subframe reinforcement\u2014essential for long-term chassis integrity. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with sharpened turn-in, this is a mechanically robust example that tracks straight and pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are exceptional.",
      "price": 34500.0,
